trans-unit.source: Represents a wsa:EndpointReference element.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en wsa:EndpointReference-element.

trans-unit.source: The wsa:EndpointReference element can be used in wst:OnBehalfOf and wp:AppliesTo elements inside of a wsp:RequestSecurityToken element to specify an endpoint reference.
trans-unit.target: Elementet wsa:EndpointReference kan brukes i wst:OnBehalfOf og wp:AppliesTo elementer i et wsp:RequestSecurityToken element til å angi en endpoint-referanse.

trans-unit.source: Supports either the WS-Addressing standard schema namespace (http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2004/08/addressing) or the WS-Addressing 1.0 schema namespace (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing) when reading.
trans-unit.target: Støtter WS-adressering standard Skjemanavneområdet (http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2004/08/addressing) eller navneområdet WS-adressering 1.0 skjemaet (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing) under lesing av.

trans-unit.source: On write only the WS-Addressing 1.0 namespace (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing) is supported.
trans-unit.target: Skriv støttes bare WS-adressering 1.0-navneområdet (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing).

trans-unit.source: For more information about the wsa:EndpointReference element, see the Web Services Addressing – Core specification.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om elementet wsa:EndpointReference, kan du se Web Services adressering – Core-spesifikasjonen.

trans-unit.source: For more information about its use in WS-Trust protocols, see the version of the WS-Trust specification that applies to your scenario.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om bruk i WS-Trust protokoller, kan du se versjonen av WS-Trust-spesifikasjon som gjelder for scenariet.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the XML elements that are contained in the endpoint reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av XML-elementer som finnes i endpoint-referanse.

trans-unit.source: The wsa:Address element is not included in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Wsa:Address-elementet er ikke inkludert i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The collection contains all of the child elements of the wsa:EndpointReference element except the wsa:Address element.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen inneholder alle de underordnede elementene for elementet wsa:EndpointReference unntatt wsa:Address-element.

trans-unit.source: The collection is populated by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.ReadFrom%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen er lagt til av den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.ReadFrom%2A>metoden.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.ReadFrom%2A>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Uri%2A>egenskapen inneholder verdien for elementet wsa:Address.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Uri%2A>

trans-unit.source: Writes the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference"></xref> as a <wsa:EndpointReference> element to the specified XML writer.
trans-unit.target: Skriver den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference"> </xref> som en <wsa:EndpointReference> elementet som angitte XML-skriveren.

trans-unit.source: Only supports writing the WS-Addressing 1.0 standard schema namespace (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing).
trans-unit.target: Støtter bare skriving navneområdet WS-adressering 1.0 standard skjemaet (http://www.w3.org/2005/08/addressing).

trans-unit.source: The wsa:Address element is written first with the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Uri%2A> property, then the other elements specified in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Details%2A> collection are written.
trans-unit.target: Elementet wsa:Address skrives med verdien for den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Uri%2A>egenskapen og de andre elementene som er angitt i den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Details%2A>samlingen skrives.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Details%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Protocols.WSTrust.EndpointReference.Uri%2A>
